g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f68df075e2b223bb87bba2be02713a7f0d7489b4","tid":203322,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:32:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幾時比埋零零柒片尾<br />\n唔知做咩著晒火 果到我地睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又係WO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%9B%B7%E6%B0%8F%E5%BA%9F%E9%93%81%E5%8E%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%259B%25B7%25E6%25B0%258F%25E5%25BA%259F%25E9%2593%2581%25E5%258E%2582&d=1ElP8QZN%2FBtuydBCWvxAMozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=611587cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%9B%B7%E6%B0%8F%E5%BA%9F%E9%93%81%E5%8E%82</a><br />\n<br />\n簡介[編輯]<br />\n是出現在由周星馳主演的香港電影國產凌凌漆粵語無刪節原版片尾花絮中的神秘場景。 主要有：<br />\n凌凌漆發現了一處暗室<br />\n<br />\n007 found sth.<br />\n廢鐵廠里爆炸四起<br />\n<br />\nexplosion<br />\n<br />\nlei's<br />\n凌凌漆在廢墟火焰中<br />\n<br />\n007 in the ruin<br />\n凌凌漆和滿身灰塵跑來的李香琴擁抱在一起<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劇終<br />\n<br />\nthe end<br />\n其他[編輯]<br />\n找不到任何介紹這個場景的資料<br />\n推測應該是國產凌凌漆為續集準備的鏡頭，但因為種種原因，最終並沒有續集上映"},{"pid":"3a3e94ff90cc73c20b3e9b5f6e4ecd3697a8e072","tid":203322,"uid":39886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:00:36.000Z","msg":"屌 果隻臨記雞都好拎黎做加長版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647e6891c17192a5a5906443e042ff2be726b96b","tid":203322,"uid":40625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T05:51:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 果隻臨記雞都好拎黎做加長版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係囉，加長版做要得國語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de48cd3eff9ef3aabdc67424edd15054ee2e97a2","tid":203322,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T05:57:18